msgid "Usage"
msgstr "使用量"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_nk.html.heex:10
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "When"
msgstr "何時"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_m.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "When a channel is moderated, only operators (+o) and voiced (+v) users can send messages. Regular users can still read but not write."
msgstr "當一個頻道被調製時,只有運算符(+o)和表達的(+v)用戶可以發送消息. 普通用戶仍然可以讀而不寫."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_i.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "When invite-only is set, users cannot join unless they are invited by an operator."
msgstr "當只設定邀請時,用戶不能加入,除非他們受到操作員的邀請."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_n.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "When set, only channel members can send messages to the channel. Non-members attempting to send will receive an error. Service messages (NickServ, ChanServ) are not affected."
msgstr "設定時,只有頻道成員才能向頻道發送消息. 非成員試圖發送會收到錯誤. 服務信息(NickServ, ChanServ)不受影響."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_r.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "When set, only users who have identified with NickServ can join the channel. Users already in the channel when +R is set are not affected."
msgstr "設定時,只有已經與NickServer識別的用戶才能加入頻道. 設置 +R 時已經在頻道中的用戶不受影響 。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_t.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "When topic lock is set, only channel operators can change the topic."
msgstr "當主題鎖定設定時,只有頻道運營商可以更改主題."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_nk.html.heex:12
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "attempt will be silently rejected. This is useful for invite-only channels that do not want to receive join requests."
msgstr "嘗試將被默默拒絕。 這對不想要接收聯合請求的只邀請頻道有用 。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_nk.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "is set, any"
msgstr "設置, 任何"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_nk.html.heex:4
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "requests to the channel."
msgstr "請求到頻道。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/channel_permissions.html.heex:111
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "&rarr; Owner (~) automatically on join"
msgstr "& rarr; 加入時自動擁有者 (~)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/channel_permissions.html.heex:123
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "(Auto Operator) &rarr; Operator (@) automatically on join"
msgstr "(自動運算符) & rarr; 運算符 (@) 自動連接"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/channel_permissions.html.heex:129
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "(Auto Voice) &rarr; Voiced (+) automatically on join"
msgstr "(Auto Voice) & rarr; 語音 (+) 自動加入"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/channel_permissions.html.heex:117
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "(Super Operator) &rarr; Operator (@) automatically on join"
msgstr "(超級運算符) & rarr; 運算符 (@) 自動連接時"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/channel_permissions.html.heex:147
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "(banned) — Banned users cannot join. Removed with"
msgstr "(被禁)——被禁用戶不能加入. 刪除方式"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/channel_permissions.html.heex:152
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "(invite-only) — Only invited users or those with ban exceptions can join."
msgstr "(invite- only)——只有被邀請的用戶或那些有禁令例外的用戶才能加入."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/channel_permissions.html.heex:159
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "(key) — Requires the correct password:"
msgstr "(關鍵)——需要正確的密碼:"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/channel_permissions.html.heex:162
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "(limit) — Channel cannot exceed the user limit."
msgstr "(限制)——頻道不能超過用戶限制."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/channel_permissions.html.heex:184
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "(moderated) — Only Voiced, Half-Operator, Operator, and Owner can speak."
msgstr "(省略)——只有語音,半操作員,操作員,和所有者才能發言."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/channel_permissions.html.heex:190
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "(no external) — Only channel members can send messages."
msgstr "(沒有外部)——只有頻道成員可以發送消息."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/chanserv.html.heex:99
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
